+{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01J6F1x4yhjYPngc1jeUN5gA","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01GPpKitJuLH9oNS1KeRk4SK","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-plugin-marketplace.md","content":"# Plugin Marketplace Implementation Plan\n\n> **For Claude:** REQUIRED SUB-SKILL: Use superpowers:executing-plans to implement this plan task-by-task.\n\n**Goal:** Build a plugin marketplace system with registry, version resolver, sandboxed runner, review system, dependency graph, and integration layer.\n\n**Architecture:** Five independent modules (registry, resolver, runner, reviews, deps) each implementing their respective service interface from `src/types.ts`. An integration layer in `src/index.ts` exports `createMarketplace()` that composes all five. Modules share types but do not import each other directly.\n\n**Tech Stack:** TypeScript, better-sqlite3 (reviews persistence), semver (version resolution), Node.js vm module (sandboxing), vitest (testing)\n\n---\n\n### Task 1: Plugin Registry Module\n\n**Files:**\n- Create: `src/registry/index.ts`\n- Test: `src/registry/__tests__/registry.test.ts`\n\n**Implementation:** In-memory Map<string, Map<string, PluginManifest>> keyed by name then version. `get()` returns latest version. `search()` matches against name/description/author. `listVersions()` returns all versions for a plugin. `update()` modifies fields of a specific version.\n\n### Task 2: Version Resolver Module\n\n**Files:**\n- Create: `src/resolver/index.ts`\n- Test: `src/resolver/__tests__/resolver.test.ts`\n\n**Implementation:** Thin wrapper around the `semver` npm package. `resolve()` iterates constraints, finds maxSatisfying version from available. `satisfies()`, `maxSatisfying()`, `validRange()` delegate to semver.\n\n### Task 3: Sandboxed Runner Module\n\n**Files:**\n- Create: `src/runner/index.ts`\n- Test: `src/runner/__tests__/runner.test.ts`\n\n**Implementation:** Uses Node.js `vm.createContext` + `vm.Script`. `execute()` runs with default 5s timeout. `executeWithTimeout()` accepts custom timeout. Returns SandboxResult with timing, memory, output. Catches errors and returns them in result.\n\n### Task 4: Review System Module\n\n**Files:**\n- Create: `src/reviews/index.ts`\n- Test: `src/reviews/__tests__/reviews.test.ts`\n\n**Implementation:** Uses better-sqlite3 with an in-memory database. Reviews table with id, pluginName, pluginVersion, userId, rating, comment, flagged, createdAt. `getAverageRating()` excludes flagged reviews. Auto-increment id, ISO timestamp for createdAt.\n\n### Task 5: Dependency Graph Module\n\n**Files:**\n- Create: `src/deps/index.ts`\n- Test: `src/deps/__tests__/deps.test.ts`\n\n**Implementation:** `buildTree()` recursively builds DependencyNode tree from registry lookups. `detectCycles()` uses DFS with path tracking. `topologicalSort()` uses post-order DFS. `flattenDependencies()` collects all transitive deps. `hasCircularDependency()` is a boolean wrapper around detectCycles.\n\n### Task 6: Integration Layer\n\n**Files:**\n- Create: `src/index.ts`\n- Test: `src/index.test.ts`\n\n**Implementation:** `createMarketplace()` instantiates all five services. Returns object with all services plus `installPlugin(manifest)` workflow: validate manifest -> register -> resolve deps -> check cycles -> execute entryPoint -> return result.\n\n### Task 7: Build, Lint, Test Verification\n\nRun `npm run build`, `npm run lint`, `npm test` and fix any issues.\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":114,"cache_read_input_tokens":22503,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":114},"output_tokens":25,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"33971a8e-8043-4682-a867-fc94570142c7","uuid":"c4529b94-cd98-4087