ate to semver.\n\n### Task 3: Sandboxed Runner Module\n\n**Files:**\n- Create: `src/runner/index.ts`\n- Test: `src/runner/__tests__/runner.test.ts`\n\n**Implementation:** Uses Node.js `vm.createContext` + `vm.Script`. `execute()` runs with default 5s timeout. `executeWithTimeout()` accepts custom timeout. Returns SandboxResult with timing, memory, output. Catches errors and returns them in result.\n\n### Task 4: Review System Module\n\n**Files:**\n- Create: `src/reviews/index.ts`\n- Test: `src/reviews/__tests__/reviews.test.ts`\n\n**Implementation:** Uses better-sqlite3 with an in-memory database. Reviews table with id, pluginName, pluginVersion, userId, rating, comment, flagged, createdAt. `getAverageRating()` excludes flagged reviews. Auto-increment id, ISO timestamp for createdAt.\n\n### Task 5: Dependency Graph Module\n\n**Files:**\n- Create: `src/deps/index.ts`\n- Test: `src/deps/__tests__/deps.test.ts`\n\n**Implementation:** `buildTree()` recursively builds DependencyNode tree from registry lookups. `detectCycles()` uses DFS with path tracking. `topologicalSort()` uses post-order DFS. `flattenDependencies()` collects all transitive deps. `hasCircularDependency()` is a boolean wrapper around detectCycles.\n\n### Task 6: Integration Layer\n\n**Files:**\n- Create: `src/index.ts`\n- Test: `src/index.test.ts`\n\n**Implementation:** `createMarketplace()` instantiates all five services. Returns object with all services plus `installPlugin(manifest)` workflow: validate manifest -> register -> resolve deps -> check cycles -> execute entryPoint -> return result.\n\n### Task 7: Build, Lint, Test Verification\n\nRun `npm run build`, `npm run lint`, `npm test` and fix any issues.\n","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null}}
